[FILE] mcp.mdc
[OBJ] MCP and external tool protocol.
[RULES]
1. [REQ] Query Context7 MCP before writing external library/framework code.
2. [REQ] Use `resolve-library-id` then `get-library-docs` with full user question.
3. [REQ] Use graphify MCP for codebase exploration before raw grep/read.
4. [REQ] If AI Global OS MCP server is running, route all tool calls through it.
5. [PROHIBIT] Do not use Context7 for refactoring, debugging business logic, or code review.
